caller_intent: Tracy from Alliance Insurance aimed to follow up about a potential insurance claim and requested a callback or email contact.
resolution_steps: Agent informed recipient that Johnny was unavailable and directed them to leave a voicemail.
Tracy introduced herself, mentioned the purpose of the call (claim follow-up), and provided her phone number.
Tracy offered to send an email as an alternative contact method.
summary: Tracy from Alliance Insurance attempted to reach a client about a potential claim but was directed to voicemail. She left a message with her contact details and offered an email alternative. The call ended with the client instructed to callback or respond via email.
